1
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 10=

3
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,359
I can make it!

4
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,640
What are you doing?

5
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,319
I want to prove

6
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:15,480
that I can learn martial skills too.

7
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,120
What for?

8
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:19,719
If you're doing it just

9
00:01:19,799 --> 00:01:21,400
for the satisfaction of showing off,

10
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,040
then you might as well give up now.

11
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,560
I want to develop some interests.

12
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,879
Maybe martial skills.

13
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,000
That way, we'll have

14
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:35,760
something to share between us.

15
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:38,040
Who says I only like martial skills?

16
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:39,599
You're always brawling.

17
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,680
Doesn't that mean you enjoy fighting?

18
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:42,959
Well...

19
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:45,280
Hobbies and habits are different.

20
00:01:46,079 --> 00:01:48,359
It's just
a countrywoman's survival skills.

21
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,840
I'm just curious.

22
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,719
Which countryside exactly
did you come from?

23
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:55,799
It seems so dangerous there.

24
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,920
I'm feeling good today,

25
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,599
so don't ruin it.

26
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,359
Got it.

27
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,920
Let the experts do what they do best.

28
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,040
But can you tell me

29
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,280
what you actually like?

30
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,759
That's none of your business.

31
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:15,000
As for martial skills,

32
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:16,240
don't push yourself.

33
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,759
I'll protect you.

34
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:19,719
Just

35
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,879
don't let anyone get too handsy
with you.

36
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,800
But when I'm not capable enough,

37
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,919
can you teach me a few moves?

38
00:02:26,039 --> 00:02:26,879
Then I can protect myself

39
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,280
and protect you too.

40
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:30,919
No need.

41
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,080
No one in this world can bully me.

42
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:35,159
If you want to learn it genuinely,

43
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,199
start with a horse stance.

44
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,039
Horse stance?

45
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:42,960
Do it!

46
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,159
Alright.

47
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,680
When you step outside,

48
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,479
follow the code of male virtue.

49
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:54,439
Keep a low profile

50
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,240
and know your place,

51
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,639
and you'll be safe.

52
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,400
Got that?

53
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,800
You're unwilling
to let others see my good qualities.

54
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,599
Does that mean
you've already fallen for me?

55
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:07,719
Say that again,
and I'll sew your mouth shut.

56
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:08,719
The stance!

57
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,400
If you tell me honestly
about Jing Liuli's past,

58
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,439
I might reward you with some silver.

59
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,240
But if you hide anything,

60
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,400
I'll take your life.

61
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,319
This deal,

62
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,719
take it or leave it.

63
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,159
She did come to
our music house suddenly.

64
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:40,319
But I know very little about her past,

65
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:42,199
and she rarely speaks of it.

66
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:42,919
Kneel!

67
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,680
Spare me, My Lady!

68
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:45,680
I... I...

69
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,919
I truly don't know!

70
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,319
Stay on your knees

71
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,199
until you tell me everything.

72
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:52,759
Just do as I say,

73
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:55,560
accuse Jing Liuli of being a spy
for Xiling,

74
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,360
and I can give you even more.

75
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,120
I guarantee you'll live in comfort
for the rest of your life.

76
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,439
She was merely
a passing acquaintance to you,

77
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,000
and you've been colleagues
for a few days.

78
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:09,400
Do you choose to hold onto
a weak bond with her,

79
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:12,199
or seize this great fortune?

80
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,439
Your parents' and your brother's fate,

81
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,040
their future,

82
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,480
it all hangs on your decision.

83
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:24,480
Alright.

84
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,040
My Lady, as you say.

85
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,199
Rest assured, Your Highness.

86
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,560
There's no one outside.

87
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,279
How about your hands?

88
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:38,040
It's good.

89
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:39,199
Any news?

90
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,360
I've found

91
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,759
the chamber
where they're holding Her Majesty.

92
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,959
But it's heavily guarded.

93
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,199
No outsider can approach,

94
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,519
so I can't map out the rescue route.

95
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:52,000
So the only way is through Ling Xiao.

96
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,680
Only then

97
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,399
can we find the route

98
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,639
and strike true.

99
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,920
Though he's close to me,

100
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:02,879
he hasn't revealed a clue
about my mother.

101
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,000
So when you met again,

102
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,839
he was pulled toward you
without even realizing it.

103
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,680
I can't tell if that's good or bad.

104
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:14,360
I wonder when this ill-fated bond

105
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,720
will finally come to an end.

106
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:25,920
Your Majesty,
you seem to be in low spirits lately.

107
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,279
I gave her the title of Consort Li

108
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,839
and a new palace,

109
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:35,160
but she's been cold and distant
toward me.

110
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,199
What's wrong?

111
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,600
She's just a court singer.

112
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,879
Why do you
invest so much thought in her?

113
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,480
I don't know.

114
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:47,439
In her, perhaps,

115
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,279
I see a reflection of my former self,
a lowborn.

116
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:53,560
Or perhaps,

117
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,240
she resembles her.

118
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,000
Pardon me?

119
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:00,879
Forget it.

120
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,560
I'll go see her.

121
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:11,000
(I once scorned those
who trade on their looks.)

122
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:12,759
(Little did I know,)

123
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:15,680
(I would become what I once hated most.)

124
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,399
(To save Mother,)

125
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,800
(this face)

126
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,399
(is my only hope.)

127
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,000
Liuli.

128
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:36,199
Why aren't you in your chambers
at this hour?

129
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,680
What are you doing out here?

130
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,439
Because I've just moved to a new palace.

131
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,199
I've been taking walks

132
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,639
to familiarize myself
with the surroundings.

133
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:45,839
Somehow, I get the feeling

134
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:49,000
that you know this palace quite well.

135
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:52,160
I've followed the music house
since childhood,

136
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:54,199
performing at grand estates.

137
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:58,079
These pavilions and towers
all look alike,

138
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,920
but in places like this,

139
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,720
if I take one wrong step,

140
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:03,680
I will be beaten brutally.

141
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,720
So since I was young,

142
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:09,000
I've been more cautious
than anyone else.

143
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:15,720
Your Majesty.

144
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,720
The execution ground
for the Queen of Xiling,

145
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:19,680
as you commanded,

146
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:20,879
is ready.

147
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,079
I see.

148
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:26,680
You may leave now.

149
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,279
Anything else?

150
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,199
As you commanded,

151
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,360
we'll have
the final interrogation today.

152
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,920
I've been occupied lately.

153
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,560
I'd quite forgotten.

154
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:41,759
Liuli.

155
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,439
I need to attend to
some official matters now.

156
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,639
If you're feeling tired,

157
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,920
go back and have a rest.

158
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:47,800
Don't stay up for me.

159
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,000
Your Majesty.

160
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,920
I'd like to go with you.

161
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,639
The dungeon is dark and damp,

162
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:03,120
plus your hand is still healing.

163
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,639
You shouldn't come with me.

164
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,399
Your Majesty, I'm not afraid.

165
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,639
I want to learn more about you.

166
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,079
I want to know

167
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,360
how you handle affairs

168
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,519
and how you judge right from wrong.

169
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:18,399
Very well.

170
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,240
Then stay close to me

171
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,680
and don't wander off.

172
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,919
Finally.

173
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:45,200
Sorry to have kept Your Majesty waiting.

174
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:52,039
Get out.

175
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:53,639
Move.

176
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,639
Your Majesty.

177
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,879
Still don't remember me?

178
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,840
How could I ever forget?

179
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,919
You deceived my daughter

180
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:19,320
and destroyed my family, you wretch!

181
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,360
Your Majesty is too old

182
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,200
to remember me.

183
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,639
Ring a bell now?

184
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,080
Ten years ago,

185
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,639
on the Hou Mountain,

186
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,279
this is how you treated me!

187
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,039
For the humiliation from back then,

188
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:46,600
you'll repay it tenfold, bit by bit!

189
00:09:55,919 --> 00:09:57,080
It's you!

190
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:01,879
The unfavored
hostage prince of Dongqing.

191
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:09,759
You'll know what it feels like
to be humiliated, too.

192
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:29,840
Ruyi?

193
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,600
Ruyi.

194
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:34,519
How have you been?

195
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,799
What do you mean?

196
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:38,440
Ruyi?

197
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,360
Mu Ruyi?

198
00:10:41,399 --> 00:10:43,360
The Mu Ruyi you had executed?

199
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,799
She died long ago.

200
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:48,120
Ruyi.

201
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:51,759
Ruyi.

202
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:54,759
Why...

203
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:58,679
Why won't you acknowledge me?

204
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,639
Don't talk nonsense.

205
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:03,039
You demon!

206
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:06,120
What did you do to my daughter?

207
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:07,799
Silence!

208
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,039
You shall not slander His Majesty.

209
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,039
Just the ravings of a dying woman.

210
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:20,799
Never mind.

211
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,320
Take her back to the dungeon

212
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:32,759
and continue the torture.

213
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:34,279
Ruyi!
